<fieldset style="margin:10px 0; padding:10px;">
  <legend>Skill Rules</legend>

  <p style="opacity:0.85; margin:0 0 10px;">
    Skills are proficiencies (including spell schools). They are not actions. Actions are Talents (Spells or Special Attacks).
  </p>

  <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:10px;">
    <label>
      Usage Notes (optional)
      <textarea
        name="system.rules"
        rows="6"
        placeholder="Notes for how this skill is used, common applications, GM guidance, etc."
      >{{system.rules}}</textarea>
    </label>
  </div>
</fieldset>
